    <fr:title text="Witness">Witness</fr:title>
    <fr:authors />
  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
    <fr:p>A <fr:em>witness</fr:em> is a value that proves that an existential proposition is true.</fr:p>
    <fr:p>For example, for the claim

<fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[\exists  x:\mathbb {Z}.x > 100]]></fr:tex>

the value <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[x=101]]></fr:tex> would be a witness.</fr:p>
  </fr:mainmatter>
